5:
Huh? It's not every day I see you in
the library, Edita. What're you
reading?
9:
Oh, this? It's yesterday's special
edition of the Oculus!
13:
It has a whole bunch of articles on
the latest fashions for female
adventurers! Weapons, armaments,
you name it!
18:
That's the Oculus for you, they've got
something for everyone.
23:
Seriously, look at this! Isn't that SICK?
I love everything this studio designs.
They're getting more and more
popular every day!
27:
Huh. You know what, this actually is
a pretty cool piece.
30:
Hey, it looks like that studio does
tours!
34:
Ooh! You like it too, eh? Let's go on
that tour together, then!
38:
I've wanted to go since forever, but
figured if I went alone, I'd just say
something stupid again... Please go
with me! PLEASE!
43:
You know what? I'm kind of curious
myself now. Let's go!
54:
This is where I do most of my design
work. Stay out of the forge in the
back, but other than that, feel free to
look at whatever.
57: W-wow! This one was in the Oculus!
62:
Ahh, it's just so... amazing! All of
them are! I'm seriously going to lose
it.
66:
I know what you mean. Being
around this much cool stuff really
gets you pumped up.
71:
Oh, I NEED this one!
Y-yikes. That price tag, though...
74:
Hey there, sir! I just want you to
know... One day I swear I'll come
here and place an order for a
custom weapon! I promise!
78:
...You really don't have a good eye
for armaments, do you?
81:
Huh?! What the hell is that supposed
to mean?!
84: Forget it. It's nothing to do with you.
89:
No, you don't get to just insult my
taste and then tell me it has nothing
to do with me!
98:
Wait a minute, this doesn't even
make sense. Are you dissing your
own item? YOU made this, you dolt.
101:
Oh, shut it! It's not like I make these
things 'cause I want to!
108:
The hell I won't! Don't talk like you
know me, girl.
110:
You ever hear of a little thing called
supply & demand? If I don't make
things people want to buy, someone
else will!
114:
Huh?! What kind of a stupid-ass
reason is that?! None of that
matters, you should just do what
you want to
122:
You know, there are some smug
adventurers out there who they
think they're hot stuff... But I'm gonna
show them who's the REAL deal!
125:
You know who I'm talking about,
don't you? Palpebra's own Levy, of
course!
135:
Whatever. I've had enough of you
two. See yourselves out.
142:
I... I just realized I'm the same as you!
I'm in no position to criticize you
when I'm doing the same thing...
150:
Still though. There's nothing lamer
than caring too much about what
other people think of you!
154:
That's why I want to change. No, I'm
DEFINITELY going to change! Just you
watch.
156:
You can too, if you want, Mr. Artisan.
There's no need to make those
weapons if your heart's not into it!
161:
...I'm sorry, my friend is just really
enthusiastic about your armaments.
164:
Thanks for letting us take a look at
the place.
167: Edita, let's get going, all right?
172:
I was out of line there too. There was
no need to take out my own issues
on you. Sorry.
174: Let me make it up to you.
181:
Well, that worked out well, huh? 
To think he's going to make you a
weapon at such a huge discount!
188:
That's why... I have to make sure 
I keep my promise.
192:
I've made up my mind! At my next
event, I'm going to tell everyone that
I'm a fan of Levy's.
197:
Really? Aren't you worried about
how people will react?
204:
If I keep doing what I have been, 
I'll probably just get sad every time 
I get on the stage. I don't think I can
stand that.
207:
Who knows if my fans will forgive
me... But I know for a fact it's better
than lying.
211:
Yeah, I can see where you're coming
from. I'm rooting for you, Edita.
219:
I need to show everyone... 
who I REALLY am.
